#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:5
msgid "Simple OAuth2 System (experimental)"
msgstr "OAuth2 시스템(실험적)"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:7
msgid ""
"Xinference builds an In-memory OAuth2 authentication and authorization "
"system using the account-password mode."
msgstr "Xinference는 계정과 비밀번호 방식을 사용하여 메모리 기반 OAuth2 인증 및 권한 부여 시스템을 구축합니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:10
msgid ""
"Since **v3.0**, Xinference enables the :ref:`advanced, database-backed "
"authentication system <user_guide_advanced_auth_system>` by default "
"(``XINFERENCE_AUTH_ADVANCED``), replacing the in-memory system described "
"below as the default behavior. On first startup, an ``admin`` account is "
"created automatically and its one-time password is printed to the server log"
" — save it, since it is not shown again."
msgstr ""
"**v3.0**\\ 부터 Xinference는 :ref:`고급 데이터베이스 기반 인증 시스템 "
"<user_guide_advanced_auth_system>`\\ (``XINFERENCE_AUTH_ADVANCED``)\\ 을 기본으로"
" 활성화하며, 아래에서 설명하는 인메모리 시스템을 대체하는 기본 동작이 됩니다. 처음 시작할 때 ``admin`` 계정이 자동으로 "
"생성되고, 일회용 비밀번호가 서버 로그에 출력됩니다 — 다시 표시되지 않으므로 반드시 저장해 두세요."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:17
msgid ""
"The simple, file-based authentication system on this page still works and is"
" not going away. To use it instead of the advanced system, set "
"``XINFERENCE_AUTH_ADVANCED=false`` and pass ``--auth-config`` as described "
"below. To disable authentication entirely, also set "
"``XINFERENCE_AUTH_ADVANCED=false`` and omit ``--auth-config``."
msgstr ""
"이 페이지에서 설명하는 간단한 파일 기반 인증 시스템은 계속 작동하며 사라지지 않습니다. 고급 시스템 대신 이를 사용하려면 "
"``XINFERENCE_AUTH_ADVANCED=false``\\ 로 설정하고 아래 설명대로 ``--auth-config``\\ 를 "
"전달하세요. 인증을 완전히 비활성화하려면 마찬가지로 ``XINFERENCE_AUTH_ADVANCED=false``\\ 로 설정하고 "
"``--auth-config``\\ 를 생략하세요."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:25
msgid "Permissions"
msgstr "권한"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:26
msgid ""
"Currently, Xinference system internally defines some interface permissions:"
msgstr "현재, Xinference 내부에서는 다음과 같은 인터페이스 권한이 정의되어 있습니다:"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:28
msgid ""
"``models:list``: Permission to list models and get models' information."
msgstr "``models:list``: 모델 목록 및 정보를 가져오는 권한."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:29
msgid "``models:read``: Permission to use models."
msgstr "`models:read`: 모델을 읽을 수 있는 권한."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:30
msgid "``models:register``: Permission to register custom models."
msgstr "``models:register``: 모델 등록 권한."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:31
msgid "``models:unregister``: Permission to unregister custom models."
msgstr "``models:unregister``: 모델 등록을 취소할 권한."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:32
msgid "``models:start``: Permission to launch models."
msgstr "``models:start``: 모델을 시작할 수 있는 권한입니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:33
msgid "``models:stop``: Permission to stop running models."
msgstr "``models:stop``: 모델을 중지할 권한입니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:34
msgid "``admin``: Administrators have permissions for all interfaces."
msgstr "``admin``: 관리자는 모든 인터페이스에 대한 권한을 가집니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:38
msgid "Startup"
msgstr "시작하기"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:39
msgid ""
"All authentication and authorization information needs to be specified and "
"loaded into memory when Xinference is started. Xinference requires a JSON-"
"formatted file with the following specific fields:"
msgstr ""
"Xinference를 시작할 때는 모든 인증 및 권한 정보를 지정해야 합니다. 현재 Xinference는 다음 특정 필드를 포함하는 "
"JSON 파일이 필요합니다:"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:78
msgid ""
"``auth_config``: This field is used to configure security-related "
"information."
msgstr "``auth_config``: 이 필드는 보안 관련 정보를 구성합니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:80
msgid ""
"``algorithm``: The algorithm used for token generation and parsing. ``HS`` "
"series algorithms are recommended. For example, ``HS256``, ``HS384`` or "
"``HS512``."
msgstr ""
"``algorithm``: 토큰 생성 및 파싱에 사용되는 알고리즘입니다. ``HS`` 계열 알고리즘(예: ``HS256``, "
"``HS384`` 또는 ``HS512``)을 사용하는 것을 권장합니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:82
msgid ""
"``secret_key``: The secret_key used for token generation and parsing. Use "
"this command to generate the secret_key adapted to the ``HS`` algorithms: "
"``openssl rand -hex 32``."
msgstr ""
"``secret_key``: 토큰 생성 및 분석에 사용되는 키입니다. 다음 명령을 사용하여 ``HS`` 시리즈 알고리즘에 적합한 키를 "
"생성할 수 있습니다: ``openssl rand -hex 32``."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:84
msgid ""
"``token_expire_in_minutes``: Reserved field indicating the expiration time "
"of the token. The current open-source version of Xinference does not check "
"the expiration time of tokens."
msgstr ""
"``token_expire_in_minutes``: 예약 필드로, 토큰 만료 시간을 나타냅니다. 현재 Xinference 오픈 소스 "
"버전에서는 토큰 만료 시간을 확인하지 않습니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:86
msgid ""
"``user_config``: This field is used to configure user and permission "
"information. Each user information is composed of these fields:"
msgstr ""
"``user_config``: 이 필드는 사용자와 권한 정보를 구성하는 데 사용됩니다. 각 사용자 정보는 다음 필드로 구성됩니다:"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:88
msgid "``username``: string field for username."
msgstr "``username``: 문자열, 사용자 이름을 나타냄"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:90
msgid "``password``: string field for password."
msgstr "``password``: 문자열, 비밀번호를 나타냄"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:92
msgid ""
"``permissions``: A list containing strings representing the permissions that"
" this user has. The permissions are described as above."
msgstr ""
"``permissions``: 문자열 리스트로, 해당 사용자가 소유한 권한을 나타냅니다. 권한 설명은 위의 권한 부분 문서에 기술된 바와"
" 같습니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:94
msgid ""
"``api_keys``: A list containing strings representing the api-keys of this "
"user. With these api-keys, user can access the xinference interfaces without"
" the need to signin. The api-key here is formatted similar to the "
"``OPENAI_API_KEY`` , always starting with ``sk-``, followed by 13 "
"alphanumeric characters."
msgstr ""
"``api_keys``: 문자열 리스트로, 해당 사용자가 소유한 api-key를 나타냅니다. 사용자는 이러한 api-key를 통해 로그인"
" 절차 없이 xinference 인터페이스에 접근할 수 있습니다. 여기서 api_key의 구성은 ``OPENAI_API_KEY``\\ 와"
" 유사하며, 항상 ``sk-``\\ 로 시작하고 그 뒤에 13개의 숫자, 대소문자 알파벳이 옵니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:97
msgid ""
"Once you have configured such a JSON file, use the ``--auth-config`` option "
"to enable Xinference with the authentication and authorization system. For "
"example, for local startup:"
msgstr ""
"이러한 JSON 파일을 설정한 후 ``--auth-config`` 옵션을 사용하여 인증 및 권한 부여 시스템이 있는 Xinference를"
" 활성화할 수 있습니다. 예를 들어, 로컬에서 시작하는 명령은 다음과 같습니다:"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:104
msgid ""
"For distributed startup, just specify this option when starting the "
"supervisor:"
msgstr "분산 환경에서는 supervisor를 시작할 때 이 옵션만 지정하면 됩니다:"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:112
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "사용"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:113
msgid ""
"For Xinference with the authentication and authorization system enabled, all"
" usage remains the same, except for the addition of a login step at the "
"beginning or using the api-key."
msgstr ""
"권한 관리가 포함된 Xinference 서비스는 일반 버전과 동일하며, 시작 단계에서 로그인 절차 또는 api-key를 사용한 인증만 "
"추가되었습니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:116
msgid "Signin"
msgstr "사용자 이름-비밀번호 기반 방식"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:117
msgid "Signin for command line users:"
msgstr "명령줄을 사용하여 로그인:"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:124
msgid "For python SDK users:"
msgstr "Python SDK를 사용하여 로그인:"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:133
msgid ""
"For web UI users, when opening the web UI, you will first be directed to the"
" login page. After logging in, you can use the web UI normally."
msgstr ""
"웹 UI 사용자의 경우, 웹 UI를 열면 먼저 로그인 페이지로 이동합니다. 로그인한 후에는 웹 UI의 기능을 정상적으로 사용할 수 "
"있습니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:136
msgid "Api-Key"
msgstr "Api-Key 인증을 사용하는 방식"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:137
msgid ""
"For command line users, just add ``--api-key`` or ``-ak`` option in the "
"command you want to use."
msgstr "명령줄 사용자의 경우, 실행하려는 명령에 ``--api-key`` 또는 ``-ak`` 옵션만 추가하면 됩니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:144
msgid ""
"For python SDK users, pass the ``api_key`` parameter when initializing the "
"client, just like the ``OPENAI`` Python client."
msgstr ""
"Python 클라이언트 사용자의 경우, 클라이언트 객체 초기화 시 ``api_key`` 매개변수를 전달하면 됩니다. 이는 "
"``OPENAI`` 클라이언트와 동일합니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:152
msgid "Xinference is also compatible with the ``OPENAI`` Python SDK as well."
msgstr "물론, Xinference는 ``OPENAI`` Python 클라이언트 사용 방식과도 완전히 호환됩니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:160
msgid ""
"For http request, pass ``Authorization: Bearer api-key`` in request header."
msgstr "HTTP 요청의 경우, 요청 헤더에 ``Authorization: Bearer api-key``\\ 를 전달하십시오."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:170
msgid "Http Status Code"
msgstr "HTTP 상태 코드"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:171
msgid "Add the following two HTTP status codes:"
msgstr "다음 두 가지 HTTP 상태 코드가 추가되었습니다:"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:173
msgid "``401 Unauthorized``: login information or token verifies failed."
msgstr "``401 Unauthorized``: 로그인 정보 또는 토큰 인증이 실패했습니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:174
msgid "``403 Forbidden``: No enough permissions when accessing interfaces."
msgstr "``403 Forbidden``: 인터페이스에 접근할 수 있는 충분한 권한이 없습니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:176
msgid ""
"For the command line, SDK, or web UI users, there will be clear information "
"prompts when encountering authorization and permissions issues."
msgstr "명령줄, SDK 또는 웹 UI 사용자의 경우 인증 및 권한 문제가 발생할 때 명확한 정보提示가 표시됩니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:179
msgid ""
"This feature is still in an experimental stage — see `Feedback`_ at the "
"bottom of this page for how to reach us with issues or suggestions."
msgstr ""
"이 기능은 아직 실험 단계입니다 — 문제나 개선 제안을 전달하는 방법은 이 페이지 하단의 `Feedback`_ 을 참고하세요."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:187
msgid "Advanced Authentication System (database-backed)"
msgstr "고급 인증 시스템(데이터베이스 기반)"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:189
msgid "The advanced authentication system, and its default-enabled status."
msgstr "고급 인증 시스템과 기본 활성화 상태."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:192
msgid ""
"Unlike the simple system above, which loads a static ``auth_config.json`` "
"file into memory, the advanced authentication system stores users, "
"permissions, API keys, and refresh tokens in a local SQLite database. It "
"supports creating/managing users and API keys at runtime through REST "
"endpoints, instead of requiring a server restart to change an "
"``auth_config.json`` file."
msgstr ""
"정적인 ``auth_config.json`` 파일을 메모리에 로드하는 위의 간단한 시스템과 달리, 고급 인증 시스템은 사용자, 권한, "
"API 키, 리프레시 토큰을 로컬 SQLite 데이터베이스에 저장합니다. ``auth_config.json`` 파일을 변경하기 위해 "
"서버를 재시작할 필요 없이, REST 엔드포인트를 통해 런타임에 사용자와 API 키를 생성/관리할 수 있습니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:199
msgid ""
"**Since v3.0, this system is enabled by default** — a fresh Xinference "
"deployment requires authentication out of the box."
msgstr ""
"**v3.0부터 이 시스템은 기본적으로 활성화됩니다** — 새로 배포한 Xinference는 별도 설정 없이도 인증이 필요합니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:203
msgid "Enabling / disabling"
msgstr "활성화 / 비활성화"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:204
msgid ""
"The advanced authentication system is controlled by the "
"``XINFERENCE_AUTH_ADVANCED`` environment variable:"
msgstr "고급 인증 시스템은 ``XINFERENCE_AUTH_ADVANCED`` 환경 변수로 제어됩니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:207
msgid ""
"Unset, or any of ``1`` / ``true`` / ``yes`` (case-insensitive): enabled (the"
" default)."
msgstr "설정하지 않았거나 ``1`` / ``true`` / ``yes``\\ (대소문자 구분 없음) 중 하나: 활성화(기본값)."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:208
msgid "Any of ``0`` / ``false`` / ``no`` (case-insensitive): disabled."
msgstr "``0`` / ``false`` / ``no``\\ (대소문자 구분 없음) 중 하나: 비활성화."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:210
msgid ""
"It is mutually exclusive with the simple system's ``--auth-config`` option —"
" passing ``--auth-config`` while ``XINFERENCE_AUTH_ADVANCED`` is (or "
"defaults to) enabled raises a startup error. To use ``--auth-config`` "
"instead, or to run with no authentication at all, set "
"``XINFERENCE_AUTH_ADVANCED=false``:"
msgstr ""
"이는 간단한 시스템의 ``--auth-config`` 옵션과 상호 배타적입니다 — ``XINFERENCE_AUTH_ADVANCED``\\"
" 가 (기본값으로) 활성화된 상태에서 ``--auth-config``\\ 를 전달하면 시작 시 오류가 발생합니다. 대신 ``--auth-"
"config``\\ 를 사용하거나 인증 없이 실행하려면 ``XINFERENCE_AUTH_ADVANCED=false``\\ 로 설정하세요."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:226
msgid "Initial admin account"
msgstr "초기 관리자 계정"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:227
msgid ""
"On first startup with the advanced system enabled, Xinference automatically "
"creates an ``admin`` user (with the ``admin`` permission) if the user table "
"is empty, and prints a one-time, randomly generated password to the server "
"log:"
msgstr ""
"고급 시스템이 활성화된 상태로 처음 시작할 때, 사용자 테이블이 비어 있으면 Xinference는 ``admin`` 권한을 가진 "
"``admin`` 사용자를 자동으로 생성하고, 무작위로 생성된 일회용 비밀번호를 서버 로그에 출력합니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:241
msgid ""
"This password is **not stored anywhere in plaintext** and is not shown again"
" — save it from the log, and change it on first login (the account is "
"flagged ``must_change_password`` until you do)."
msgstr ""
"이 비밀번호는 **평문으로 어디에도 저장되지 않으며** 다시 표시되지 않습니다 — 로그에서 저장해 두고, 처음 로그인할 때 "
"변경하세요(변경할 때까지 계정에는 ``must_change_password`` 플래그가 설정됩니다)."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:246
msgid "Secrets and storage locations"
msgstr "시크릿 및 저장 위치"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:247
msgid ""
"The advanced system needs a JWT signing secret and an encryption key (used "
"to encrypt stored API keys at rest), plus a database file. All three can be "
"overridden with environment variables; if you don't set them, Xinference "
"generates and persists them automatically on first run under "
"``XINFERENCE_HOME`` (``~/.xinference`` by default):"
msgstr ""
"고급 시스템에는 JWT 서명용 시크릿, 저장된 API 키를 암호화하는 데 사용되는 암호화 키, 그리고 데이터베이스 파일이 필요합니다. 이"
" 세 가지는 모두 환경 변수로 재정의할 수 있으며, 설정하지 않으면 Xinference가 처음 실행할 때 "
"``XINFERENCE_HOME``(기본값 ``~/.xinference``) 아래에 자동으로 생성하고 저장합니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:256
msgid "Purpose"
msgstr "용도"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:257
msgid "Environment variable"
msgstr "환경 변수"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:258
msgid "Default location"
msgstr "기본 위치"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:259
msgid "JWT signing secret"
msgstr "JWT 서명 시크릿"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:260
msgid "``XINFERENCE_AUTH_JWT_SECRET_KEY``"
msgstr "``XINFERENCE_AUTH_JWT_SECRET_KEY``"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:261
msgid "``<XINFERENCE_HOME>/auth/jwt_secret_key`` (auto-generated)"
msgstr "``<XINFERENCE_HOME>/auth/jwt_secret_key``\\ (자동 생성)"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:262
msgid "API key encryption key"
msgstr "API 키 암호화 키"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:263
msgid "``XINFERENCE_AUTH_ENCRYPTION_KEY``"
msgstr "``XINFERENCE_AUTH_ENCRYPTION_KEY``"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:264
msgid "``<XINFERENCE_HOME>/auth/encryption_key`` (auto-generated)"
msgstr "``<XINFERENCE_HOME>/auth/encryption_key``\\ (자동 생성)"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:265
msgid "User/API key database"
msgstr "사용자/API 키 데이터베이스"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:266
msgid "``XINFERENCE_AUTH_DB_PATH``"
msgstr "``XINFERENCE_AUTH_DB_PATH``"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:267
msgid "``<XINFERENCE_HOME>/auth/auth.db``"
msgstr "``<XINFERENCE_HOME>/auth/auth.db``"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:269
msgid ""
"Auto-generated secrets are written once and reused on subsequent restarts, "
"so existing JWTs and encrypted API keys keep working across restarts. In a "
"distributed deployment (supervisor + workers), make sure all processes that "
"run the RESTful API share the same ``XINFERENCE_HOME`` (or set the same "
"explicit environment variables), so they agree on the same secrets and "
"database."
msgstr ""
"자동 생성된 시크릿은 한 번만 기록되고 이후 재시작 시 재사용되므로, 기존 JWT와 암호화된 API 키는 재시작 후에도 계속 작동합니다."
" 분산 배포(supervisor + worker) 환경에서는 RESTful API를 실행하는 모든 프로세스가 동일한 "
"``XINFERENCE_HOME``\\ 을 공유하도록(또는 동일한 환경 변수를 명시적으로 설정하도록) 하여, 동일한 시크릿과 "
"데이터베이스를 사용하도록 하세요."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:277
msgid "Advanced-system permissions"
msgstr "고급 시스템 권한"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:278
msgid ""
"The advanced system uses the same permission names as the simple system "
"(``models:list``, ``models:read``, ``models:register``, "
"``models:unregister``, ``models:start``, ``models:stop``, ``admin``), plus "
"additional scopes for managing the advanced system itself:"
msgstr ""
"고급 시스템은 간단한 시스템과 동일한 권한 이름(``models:list``, ``models:read``, "
"``models:register``, ``models:unregister``, ``models:start``, "
"``models:stop``, ``admin``)을 사용하며, 고급 시스템 자체를 관리하기 위한 추가 범위를 제공합니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:283
msgid ""
"``keys:create``: Permission to create API keys (for oneself, or for others "
"when combined with ``keys:manage``)."
msgstr ""
"``keys:create``: API 키를 생성할 수 있는 권한(자신을 위해, 또는 ``keys:manage``\\ 와 결합하면 다른 "
"사용자를 위해서도 가능)."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:284
msgid ""
"``keys:manage``: Permission to list, update, delete, and reveal any user's "
"API keys."
msgstr "``keys:manage``: 모든 사용자의 API 키를 조회, 수정, 삭제 및 표시할 수 있는 권한."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:285
msgid ""
"``users:manage``: Permission to create, update, delete users, and manage "
"their permissions."
msgstr "``users:manage``: 사용자를 생성, 수정, 삭제하고 권한을 관리할 수 있는 권한."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:286
msgid ""
"``cache:list`` / ``cache:delete``: Permissions to list/delete cached model "
"files."
msgstr "``cache:list`` / ``cache:delete``: 캐시된 모델 파일을 조회/삭제할 수 있는 권한."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:287
msgid ""
"``virtualenv:list`` / ``virtualenv:delete``: Permissions to list/delete per-"
"model virtual environments."
msgstr ""
"``virtualenv:list`` / ``virtualenv:delete``: 모델별 가상 환경을 조회/삭제할 수 있는 권한."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:288
#, fuzzy
msgid "``admin``: Administrators have all of the above."
msgstr "``admin``: 관리자는 모든 인터페이스에 대한 권한을 가집니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:290
msgid ""
"A caller may only grant permissions they themselves hold — for example, a "
"user with only ``users:manage`` cannot grant ``admin`` to someone else."
msgstr ""
"호출자는 자신이 가진 권한만 부여할 수 있습니다 — 예를 들어 ``users:manage`` 권한만 가진 사용자는 다른 사람에게 "
"``admin`` 권한을 부여할 수 없습니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:294
msgid "Login and API-key usage"
msgstr "로그인 및 API 키 사용 방법"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:295
msgid ""
"Login and API-key usage (signin, ``--api-key``, ``Authorization: Bearer`` "
"header, OpenAI-SDK compatibility) work the same way as described in the "
"`Usage`_ section above for the simple system."
msgstr ""
"로그인 및 API 키 사용 방법(로그인, ``--api-key``, ``Authorization: Bearer`` 헤더, OpenAI "
"SDK 호환성)은 위의 간단한 시스템의 `Usage`_ 섹션에서 설명한 것과 동일한 방식으로 작동합니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:300
msgid "Managing users and API keys"
msgstr "사용자 및 API 키 관리"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:301
msgid ""
"Once logged in as a user with the ``users:manage`` and/or ``keys:manage`` "
"permission (the bootstrap ``admin`` account has both), you can manage users "
"and API keys through REST endpoints under ``/v1/admin``, for example:"
msgstr ""
"``users:manage`` 및/또는 ``keys:manage`` 권한을 가진 사용자로 로그인하면(초기 ``admin`` 계정은 두 "
"권한을 모두 가지고 있습니다), ``/v1/admin`` 아래의 REST 엔드포인트를 통해 사용자와 API 키를 관리할 수 있습니다. "
"예:"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:319
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Other supported endpoints include listing/updating/deleting users "
"(``/v1/admin/users``, ``/v1/admin/users/{user_id}``), changing a user's "
"password (``/v1/admin/users/{user_id}/password``), and listing, updating, "
"deleting, and revealing API keys (``/v1/admin/keys``, "
"``/v1/admin/keys/{key_id}``, ``/v1/admin/keys/{key_id}/reveal``)."
msgstr ""
"지원되는 다른 엔드포인트에는 사용자 조회/수정/삭제(``/v1/admin/users``, "
"``/v1/admin/users/{user_id}``), 사용자 비밀번호 "
"변경(``/v1/admin/users/{user_id}/password``), API 키 "
"조회/수정/삭제/표시(``/v1/admin/keys``, ``/v1/admin/keys/{key_id}``, "
"``/v1/admin/keys/{key_id}/reveal``)가 있습니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:326
msgid "Behavior notes"
msgstr "동작 관련 참고 사항"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:329
msgid "Permission changes take effect without re-login"
msgstr "권한 변경은 재로그인 없이 즉시 적용됩니다"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:330
msgid ""
"Route scope checks read the user's **current** permissions from the database"
" on every request, not the scopes baked into the JWT at login. Granting or "
"revoking a permission takes effect on the user's next API call — no re-login"
" required. This applies to JWT-based browser sessions; API keys are also "
"live-read (they always have been)."
msgstr ""
"라우트 범위 검사는 로그인 시 JWT에 포함된 범위가 아니라, 매 요청마다 데이터베이스에서 사용자의 **현재** 권한을 읽어옵니다. "
"권한을 부여하거나 취소하면 사용자의 다음 API 호출부터 바로 적용됩니다 — 재로그인이 필요하지 않습니다. 이는 JWT 기반 브라우저 "
"세션에 적용되며, API 키 역시 이전부터 실시간으로 확인되었습니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:337
msgid "Configurable access-token lifetime"
msgstr "설정 가능한 액세스 토큰 유효 기간"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:338
msgid ""
"The access-token lifetime defaults to 30 minutes and can be overridden with "
"the ``XINFERENCE_ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRE_MINUTES`` environment variable:"
msgstr ""
"액세스 토큰의 유효 기간은 기본적으로 30분이며, ``XINFERENCE_ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRE_MINUTES`` 환경 "
"변수로 재정의할 수 있습니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:345
msgid ""
"A shorter lifetime shrinks the token-theft window. The refresh token "
"lifetime is 7 days and is not currently configurable."
msgstr ""
"유효 기간을 짧게 설정하면 토큰 탈취 시 악용 가능한 시간이 줄어듭니다. 리프레시 토큰의 유효 기간은 7일이며 현재는 설정을 변경할 수 "
"없습니다."

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:349
msgid "Feedback"
msgstr "피드백"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:350
msgid ""
"This feature is still in an experimental stage. Feel free to provide "
"feedback on usage issues or improvement suggestions through `GitHub issues "
"<https://github.com/xorbitsai/inference/issues>`_ or `our Telegram group "
"<https://t.me/+nCNpwmySwk9iYmI1>`_."
msgstr ""
"이 기능은 실험 단계에 있습니다. `GitHub issues "
"<https://github.com/xorbitsai/inference/issues>`_ 또는 `Telegram 그룹 "
"<https://t.me/+nCNpwmySwk9iYmI1>`_ 을 통해 피드백과 제안을 제공해 주시기 바랍니다."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If you don't have authentication and authorization requirements, you can use"
#~ " Xinference as before, without any changes."
#~ msgstr "인증 및 권한 부여 요구 사항이 없다면 이전과 같이 Xinference를 변경 없이 사용할 수 있습니다."

#~ msgid "Note"
#~ msgstr "주의"
